article.headline: Army defeats Le Moyne 68-51

images.caption: Luke Sutherland rocks the rim with jam

article.story: WEST POINT, N.Y. -- — Blake Barker had 20 points in Army's 68-51 win against Le Moyne on Tuesday night. Barker also added five rebounds for the Black Knights (2-7). Josh Scovens added 16 points while going 7 of 12 from the floor, including 1 for 4 from 3-point range, and 1 for 4 from the line, and also had seven rebounds and three blocks. Ryan Curry shot 5 for 9, including 1 for 4 from beyond the arc to finish with 11 points. The Dolphins (3-6) were led in scoring by Luke Sutherland, who finished with 17 points. Ocypher Owens added 12 points and eight rebounds for Le Moyne. AJ Dancier also put up nine points. NEXT UP Army's next game is Friday against Harvard on the road. Le Moyne visits Binghamton on Saturday. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
